== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[711]] {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – Under the imperial edict of {{ill|Emperor Genmei|ja|元明天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}, Tai-an Maro began compiling the 【Kojiki】. * {{ill|Jōō|ja|承応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1652]] {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – Following the ascension of {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家綱|qq=draft|qq=}}, the era name was changed from {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to Jōō. == Births == * [[Eiroku]] 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1562]] {{ill|February 15|ja|2月15日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Maeda Toshinaga|ja|前田利長|qq=draft|qq=}}, 2nd lord of the Kaga Domain (d. [[1614]]). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1866]] {{ill|February 26|ja|2月26日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kawaguchi Ekai|ja|河口慧海|qq=draft|qq=}}, a Buddhist scholar and explorer of Tibet (d. [[1945]]). * [[Meiji era]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1869]] {{ill|February 22|ja|2月22日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Okada Saburōsuke|ja|岡田三郎助|qq=draft|qq=}}, a Western-style painter (d. [[1939]]). == Deaths == * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1863]] {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Serizawa Kamo|ja|芹沢鴨|qq=draft|qq=}}, commander of the Shinsengumi (born [[1826]]).
