* {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1866]] {{ill|February 26|ja|2月26日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kawaguchi Ekai|ja|河口慧海|qq=draft|qq=}}, a Buddhist scholar and explorer of Tibet (d. [[1945]]).
* [[Meiji era]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1869]] {{ill|February 22|ja|2月22日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Okada Saburōsuke|ja|岡田三郎助|qq=draft|qq=}}, a Western-style painter (d. [[1939]]).
== Deaths ==
